    public class CarbonDigitalInput
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.DigitalInput
    Custom DigitalInput object that allows the inversion of the result of the 'get' method by overriding it.

    Nick

    • Constructor Detail

      • CarbonDigitalInput

        public CarbonDigitalInput(int channel)
        Constructs a CarbonDigitalInput that acts identically to DigitalInput, defaulting to NO inversion.
        Parameters:
        channel - The DIO channel that this digital input is on.

      • CarbonDigitalInput

        public CarbonDigitalInput(int channel,
                  boolean inv)
        Constructs a CarbonDigitalInput that may be inverted based on the 'inv' parameter. An inverted CarbonDigitalInput will return the opposite reading when calling 'get()' than a DigitalInput.
        Parameters:
        channel - The DIO channel that this digital input is on.
        inv - True to invert the reading of this input, false to stay the same.
